    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318420/extras/bea6ef695d567bafac69ef4e3a78b73b.avif?t=1684861484\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br>A fast-paced, Egyptian-themed jousting tournament recalls 1980's classic arcade action.<br><br><strong>Glypha</strong>, the classic shareware game on the early Macintosh, now landed in the 21st Century ... but not too much. It still has that classic early Mac look, but 21st Century hardware acceleration, gameplay and feel. (The consensus seems to be that it is a wee bit harder now.)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game play:</h2><br>You control your player with only three controls:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Left</strong> <i>(player goes to the left)</i><br></li><li><strong>Right</strong> <i>(player goes right)</i><br></li><li><strong>Flap</strong> <i>(your bird flaps to climb)</i></li></ul>To do battle with your opponents, collide with them.<br><br>But be careful, <strong>whoever's weapon is higher</strong> than the other's <strong>wins</strong> the battle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318420/extras/2f43c93b926ed96a844b884c2be7fb7c.avif?t=1684861484\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Opponents:</h2><br>There are a number of opponents — some more challenging than others. Should you survive long enough you'll find out just how challenging. Points for defeating an opponent are shown below:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318420/extras/fe0459b2434a211a9243e6a52feb33b5.avif?t=1684861484\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Additionall controls allow you to:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Pause</strong> <i>(pause and unpause the game)</i><br></li><li><strong>Fullscreen</strong> <i>(toggle fullscreen)</i></li></ul>",
